What is Applicant Tracking Software?

Applicant Tracking software allows organizations to easily manage the hiring process by maintaining a database of applicant and job information.

Related Software Categories:

  • Human Resource Software
  • Reference Check Software
  • Video Interviewing Software
  • Talent Management Software
  • Recruiting Software
  • Performance Management System Software
  • Onboarding Software
  • Job Board Software
